                            <comment id="13073987" author="thofman" created="Thu, 4 Jun 2015 03:25:41 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Also incorporates &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/JGRP-1932&quot; title=&quot;Race condition - MERGE2 with TUNNEL transport is not merging&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JGRP-1932&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;JGRP-1932&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13074545" author="thofman" created="Fri, 5 Jun 2015 04:51:05 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Please un-ignore org.jboss.as.test.clustering.tunnel.singleton.SingletonTunnelTestCase when this upgrade is performed (in case it would already be merged - it&apos;s being added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-4724&quot; title=&quot;Port SingletonTunnelTestCase from EAP6 to WildFly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WFLY-4724&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WFLY-4724&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13074556" author="thofman" created="Fri, 5 Jun 2015 05:06:49 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Ignore above comment. The test is blocked by another issue, I will just wait when those are merged and open a PR then.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13083943" author="rhusar" created="Thu, 25 Jun 2015 12:04:54 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Update: so this never worked for 9.x, so we really need to pull this in for 9.x to work on OpenShift. We would need the release soon though otherwise we will have to push it for 9.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13084013" author="fjuma" created="Thu, 25 Jun 2015 14:00:19 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Took a closer look at the previous 9.x versions. Just a minor clarification on this - WildFly 9.0.0.Alpha1 actually used JGroups 3.4.5.Final. Thus, this was the only 9.x version for which clustering worked fine on OpenShift (since this doesn&apos;t include the fix for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/JGRP-1885&quot; title=&quot;bind_addr of 0.0.0.0 should throw an exception&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JGRP-1885&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;JGRP-1885&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Clustering on OpenShift hasn&apos;t worked for any other 9.x release since then (since JGroups was updated to 3.6.x in these releases).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13084292" author="rhusar" created="Fri, 26 Jun 2015 10:02:05 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the clarification.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13084790" author="rhusar" created="Tue, 30 Jun 2015 03:29:47 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
